	<defName>WVC_DustAngel</defName>
	<!-- <label>dust angel</label> -->
	<label>featherdust</label>
	<description>Featherdusts are an undead sub-xenotype, despite strong genetic differences they still remain within this xenotype. Their bodies are dependent on a biological resource called dust. Dust greatly affects their metabolism and at low levels they get hungry faster. They have innate mechanitor abilities and a slightly wild disposition. They are immune to most diseases, and the non-stable mutations of the undead do not show up on them. However, unlike their close relatives, their death is always the end.</description>
